  A  number  of  special  initiatives  have  been 

taken to change the lives of farmers under the leadership of hon'ble Prime Minister 

Shri  Narendra  Modi.  Irrigation  facility  has  improved.  Availability  of  seeds  and 

fertilizers  has  been  ensured.  Target  has  been  set  for  improving  the  farm 

productivity  by  issuing Soil  Health  Card.  'Per  Drop  More Corp' scheme  has  been 

launched.  It  is  the  intention  of  the  hon'ble  prime  Minister  to  make  meaningful 

efforts for doubling the income of the farmers.  

 

